Doomscrolling/ Doomsurfing (Noun)

Meaning-    Doomscrolling and doomsurfing are new terms referring to the tendency to continue to surf or scroll through bad news, even though that news is saddening, disheartening, or depressing.

Example-  If you are addicted to doomscrolling/ doomsurfing, try jumping straight out of bed in the morning rather than reaching for your phone.
